.SH COMPATIBILITY
.PP
These functions are compatible with
.I OpenSS7
with the following portability considerations:
.IP \(em \w'\(em\(em'u
These are
.IR OpenSS7 -specific
functions and should not be used by portable
.I STREAMS
drivers and modules.
The more common
.I SVR 4.2 MP
functions should be used in their stead.
.IP \(em
These functions
are provided for source level compatibility with
.I OpenSS7
for the purpose of porting
.I OpenSS7
drivers to
.BR Linux .
.IP \(em
These functions
only provide functionality comparable to
.I OpenSS7
for use by
.I STREAMS
drivers and modules.
Any and all functionality provided by
these functions
in support of
.RI non- STREAMS
devices are not supported.
.PP
See
.BR STREAMS (9)
for additional compatibility considerations.
